Package graph Description

Package that implements the graph and all the information related with it.

The graph is implemented using a adjacency list that saves all the information related with the edges (identifier of the edge, the repective weight and pheromone level). The adjacency list is implemented in an array of Node and each node has a list of Weight to store the neighbors.

The Graph also implements the methods define in the an interface.

Author:
Pedro Mendes, Rui Livramento, Francisco Costa
See Also:
Graph, Node, Weight
